      "content": "but you said it's okay to acknowledge it... and it feels so much more than just grief. it feels like the only logical way to get some peace. like there's no point in trying to fix something that's already broken. if everything is just going to be this empty and heavy, why even keep carrying it? it just feels like walking in circles for nothing.",
